name: London Is Moving
description: This digital image is the only thing that exists of this artwork as far as I know. I have no idea if it still exists in reality. It was also a very large piece made in 1999. This image is a digital composite of black and white analogue prints taken of the original painting. The image is in high resolution. See more of my art on https://www.instagram.com/chrisfraserart/ Follow me on twitter: https://twitter.com/atomicparadise
